  "reference_number": "INU0401",
  "remarks": "\nThe IRAN ALUMINIUM COMPANY is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: The Iran Aluminium Company is or has been providing aluminium powder used in solid rocket fuel. This could contribute to a relevant nuclear activity, namely the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or use for, Iran.  \n",
